Package swingtree.api.mvvm

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Val<T>
    A read only view on a value which can be observed by the Swing-Tree UI to dynamically update UI components for you.
    ValDelegate<T>
    Implementations of this are passed to VarAction lambdas exposing certain context information to the lambda, like the current value of the property, the previous one as well as access to a limit list of historic values.
    Vals<T>
    An immutable list of immutable MVVM properties.
    ValsDelegate<T>  
    Var<T>
    A mutable wrapper for a value which can be observed by the Swing-Tree UI to dynamically update UI components for you, as well as trigger an action inside your view model.
    VarAction<T>
    A VarAction can be registered on a Var to be executed when the value of the property is changed by the UI to which it is bound.
    Vars<T>
    A list of mutable properties.
    Viewable  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractVariable<T>
    The base implementation for both Var and Val interfaces.
    AbstractVariables<T>
